{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"010375e6ac","title":"关于田碧云的主要错误事实","origin":"贵州省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"496fb0129d","index":0,"year":1961,"month":3,"day":6,"articleId":"010375e6ac"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"8c19e43293","name":"[中共沿河县委监委]"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd6b36f8c0","type":"title","text":"关于田碧云的主要错误事实","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"147f9c4258","type":"authors","text":"[中共沿河县委监委]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"3934e1ce92","type":"paragraph","text":"田碧云，男，28岁，沿河县人，家庭成分地主，个人船工，中共党员，解放后，随祖父田世登（地主）生活，解放后混入担任初级社主任，杨柳队队长，分支部书记等职。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"5a2122617d","type":"paragraph","text":"一，59年渡难关时，与地主田泽云（食堂会计），田贵安兵痞三人勾结组成小集团，公开说：多劳多吃，少劳少吃，不劳不吃的口号下，造成疾病和死亡的计57人。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"c28229f5a0","type":"paragraph","text":"二、直接人命三条。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"3ec8bdae08","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）他的兄弟田泽云，田保荣与他三人亲手打死一人肖太荣，为根扁担，三人毒打肖太荣一顿，睡了两个月就死了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"24703d9970","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）在渡难关时，李三春（瞎子）吃了食堂里的红苕叶，被田碧云吊起，吊后8天就死了。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"683cc57d77","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）逼死马德云，叫马到红花去挖蕨根，当时马有病要求不去，被田逼去，就死在红花盖了。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"a801c1cb89","type":"paragraph","text":"三、翻箱倒柜7户。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"3073698851","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 渡难关时，集体贪污红苕700斤，包谷120斤。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"7864c05556","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 对政府不满意，三反撤职后，他说：“太阳照到我这方来时，再来一过","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"f88ea73080","type":"paragraph","text":"以上材料是在斗争会上承认说是他自己干的。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"},{"id":"da221a5c83","type":"paragraph","text":" 61年3月6日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac"}],"page":{"id":"42d697cdd8","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"010375e6ac","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}